lunar program and the agencys other accomplishments he said and 
they couldnt understand why it nasa was being torn down and 
raked over the coals after the accident 
with nasa now in the final stages of preparation for returning 
the shuttle fleet to flight mcculla said the era of what he called 
nasa bashing news stories is over 
the stories now look toward the future he said 
