<TEXT>
in a television news commercial filmed in 
documentary style a camera takes the viewer into a hospital past 
waiting news reporters in the corridors and up to the rooftop 
heliport 
a trenchcoated reporter is interviewing an accident victim as 
he is being eased onto a stretcher and the victim has been brought 
